text: Nahid Kiani (, born 1 August 1998 in Isfahan) is an Iranian taekwondo athlete. She won bronze medals at the 2016 Asian Championships and 2018 Asian Games. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian female taekwondo practitioners Category:Asian Games medalists in taekwondo Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Iran Category:Taekwondo practitioners at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Taekwondo Championships medalists
